## Orden de implementación

1. Migración → Modelo → Factory
2. `ClaimJobController` → `CompleteJobController` → `FailJobController`
3. Actualizar `routes/assistant-internal.php`
4. Modificar `ProcessAssistantMessage.php`
5. `SweepStuckJobs.php` → actualizar `routes/console.php`
6. Node: `sleep.ts` → modificar `LaravelClient.ts` → `AssistantJobPoller.ts` → modificar `index.ts`
7. Tests PHP → Tests Node

